<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Bienvenido - PassPort Inc.</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #10141a;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
      background: #1b1f29;
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      width: 350px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #00bcd4;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    p {
      color: #ccc;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    a {
      display: block;
      background: #00bcd4;
      color: #000;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    a:hover {
      background: #0097a7;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #888;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>PassPort Inc.</h1>
    <p>Bienvenido a la plataforma. ¿Qué deseas hacer?</p>

    <a href="/login">Iniciar sesión</a>
    <a href="/register">Registrarme</a>

    <div class="footer">
      Proyecto Challenge © 2025
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
